{"text_id":159815,"tokens":["The"," main"," content"," of"," AI","-","based"," Japanese"," Short","-","answer"," Scoring"," and"," Support"," System"," is"," as"," below",":"," ","1","."," We"," have"," developed"," an"," automated"," Japanese"," short","-","answer"," scoring"," and"," support"," machine"," for"," new"," National"," Center"," written"," test"," exams","."," ","2","."," Our"," approach"," is"," based"," on"," the"," fact"," that"," recognizing"," textual"," entail","ment"," and","/","or"," syn","onymy"," has"," been"," almost"," impossible"," for"," several"," years","."," ","3","."," The"," system"," generates"," automated"," scores"," on"," the"," basis"," of"," evaluation"," criteria"," or"," rub","rics",","," and"," human"," rat","ers"," revise"," them","."," ","4","."," The"," system"," determines"," semantic"," similarity"," between"," the"," model"," answers"," and"," the"," actual"," written"," answers"," as"," well"," as"," a"," certain"," degree"," of"," semantic"," identity"," and"," implication","."," ","5","."," Owing"," to"," the"," need"," for"," the"," scoring"," results"," to"," be"," classified"," at"," multiple"," levels",","," we"," use"," random"," forests"," to"," utilize"," many"," predictors"," effectively"," rather"," than"," use"," support"," vector"," machines","."," ","6","."," An"," experimental"," prototype"," operates"," as"," a"," web"," system"," on"," a"," Linux"," computer","."," ","7","."," We"," compared"," human"," scores"," with"," the"," automated"," scores"," for"," a"," case"," in"," which"," ","3","--","6"," allotment"," points"," were"," placed"," in"," ","8"," categories"," of"," a"," social"," studies"," test"," as"," a"," trial"," examination","."," ","8","."," The"," differences"," between"," the"," scores"," were"," within"," one"," point"," for"," ","7","0","--","9","0"," percent"," of"," the"," data"," when"," high"," semantic"," judgment"," was"," not"," needed","."," The"," results"," showed"," tha